subject: JUnit 4.8.1 is released: bug fix
msgSnippet: JUnit 4.8.1 has been released, fixing major bugs in the documentation and implementation of categories.  Thanks to our users for being on top of things.
messageBody:
JUnit 4.8.1 has been released, fixing major bugs in the documentation
and implementation of categories. Thanks to our users for being on
top of things.

http://kentbeck.github.com/junit/doc/ReleaseNotes4.8.1.html

and the javadoc at

http://kentbeck.github.com/junit/javadoc/4.8.1/

and download from

http://github.com/KentBeck/junit/downloads

Share and Enjoy,

David Saff
